pyspark.sql.functions.lcase

Returns str with all characters changed to lowercase.

Parameters
str : Column or str
        Input column or strings.

Examples


spark.range(1).select(lcase(sf.lit("Spark"))).show()
+------------+
|lcase(Spark)|
+------------+
|       spark|
+------------+

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

pyspark.sql.functions.ucase

Returns str with all characters changed to uppercase.

Parameters
str : Column or str
        Input column or strings.

Examples

spark.range(1).select(ucase(sf.lit("Spark"))).show()
+------------+
|ucase(Spark)|
+------------+
|       SPARK|
+------------+
